{"tid":1750724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家做好心理準備，呢幾日可以影響成個運動","createTime":"2019-11-24T13:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T18:00:10.000Z","uid":158973,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"508f131fbbc5dc2d1b4aa22f2e7c42755595b18c","tid":1750724,"uid":158973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:20:59.000Z","msg":"為左理大手足同選舉，呢排已經分化得好勁<br />\n今次贏好輸好，支持投白票同大力反對佢地既一定仲會繼續嘈<br />\n加上<br />\n如果輸左會出巨大無力感<br />\n如果贏左大家亦可能會比左啲心機去慶祝，其實唔係咩問題，不過之後亦可能有人會指責大家忘記運動目標，到時又再嘈過<br />\n<br />\n好多可能性<br />\n亂，我覺得好大可能<br />\n所以純粹希望大家<span style=\"color: red;\">做好心理準備</span>，捱過呢幾日<br />\n之後重整軍心，繼續兄弟爬山<br />\n香港人麻煩記住<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c200cf60b58a7c3e7f3d4da7c8c89cb0f9085e","tid":1750724,"uid":158973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:22:31.000Z","msg":"希望大家唔好自亂陣腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3069517c07387477b1edeeba5072fd16923a94","tid":1750724,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得盡咗力就得<br />\n始終贏咗都唔代表香港有救<br />\n只係打到建制派一巴<br />\n同埋顯示民意"},{"pid":"76ab92e82b187049d16d788b6384e4d198b99ac2","tid":1750724,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ad1ccfbdac635ac30d1da29bc84734d99fbbc5f","tid":1750724,"uid":158973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"0daa49f6d488cf239999d561c1d1293a78ef64b3","tid":1750724,"uid":158973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep